---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Container from '../components/primitives/Container.astro';
---
<Base title="Thee Rainers — The Operator">
  <section class="py-20 bg-bg">
    <Container>
      <h1 class="font-bold text-navy text-6xl mb-8">Composure is a physical state.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted max-w-2xl mb-12">I left the coach and kept winning, because structure beats dependence. That structure is what I hand you.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <img src="/images/rainers-first-fight.jpg" alt="Rainers first fight post-coach" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
        <p class="text-lg">My path through Aikido, skating, and dance taught me one thing: motion without structure is just noise. Boxing is the discipline where I finally codified the noise into a repeatable operating system.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="my-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Six joints. One chain.</h2>
        <img src="/images/kineticchain.png" alt="The Kinetic Chain" class="w-full" />
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted">If any joint leaks, the punch leaks. We build from the ground up.</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</Base>
